      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just never stops. the nerves, the burning... it's like being awake inside a fire 24/7. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting to exist when existing just means more of this. sometimes i just stare at the wall and think how much easier it would be if everything was just... quiet. permanently.",
